# SIXMEN — Skill routing

> Skills có `disable-model-invocation` — agent **Read** file skill khi match bảng dưới (không chỉ nhắc user @mention).

## Orchestrator (task ERP mới / resume)

| Nền tảng | Làm gì |
|----------|--------|
| **Cursor** | Gõ **`/orchestrator`** — agent **Read `AGENTS.md` trước** → `.cursor/commands/orchestrator.md` → `sixmen-orchestrator/SKILL.md` |
| **Khác** | Read `AGENTS.md` + `.cursor/skills/sixmen-orchestrator/SKILL.md` (prompt khởi động trong AGENTS) |

Human-control / HO gate / artifact chain: skill orchestrator là canonical; command là ritual rút gọn.

## Route map

| Tình huống | Read skill |
|------------|------------|
| Task ERP mới, scope chưa rõ, multi-role | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-orchestrator/SKILL.md` *(ưu tiên `/orchestrator` trên Cursor)* |
| Task brief, DoD, scope IN/OUT | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-it-manager/SKILL.md` |
| Kiến trúc, boundary, API/DB impact | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-architect/SKILL.md` |
| ERD, migration note, index/FK | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-database/SKILL.md` |
| Laravel Service, Policy, Controller | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-backend/SKILL.md` |
| Filament, Livewire UI | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-frontend/SKILL.md` |
| Pest, regression, post-feature gate | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-qa/SKILL.md` |
| Deploy, backup, env | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-devops/SKILL.md` |
| BRD, AC, user guide | `.cursor/skills/sixmen-ba/SKILL.md` |

## Artifact trước implement

1. Tạo `artifacts/{Task-ID}/` + `00-gate-status.md` + `01-task-brief.md`
2. Schema → `04-migration-note.md` + Human Owner **trước** DDL
3. Code task xong → `@sixmen-qa` gate; chạy `validate-artifacts.ps1 -TaskId {Task-ID} -Strict`

## Validate scripts

| Script | Khi nào |
|--------|---------|
| `.cursor/bootstrap/validate-artifacts.ps1` | Trước báo task xong |
| `.cursor/bootstrap/validate-task-log.ps1` | Trước paste Task_Log lên Sheet |
